{"data":{"site":{"meta":{"title":"Yentsen Liu","description":"Interface/Empowerment/Democracy Design Portfolio by Yentsen Liu","url":"https://yentsenliu.com","author":"Yentsen Liu","twitter":"ansinlau","adsense":""}},"post":{"id":"f5088d76-ffae-58d0-96ec-7611ef3b91e7","html":"<hr>\n<h1>How design could help interactively visualise data, and how design can lower the threshold of transforming raw data into conprehensive information?</h1>\n<p>By redesigning the user interface of Statfin, the official statistics database of Finland, the project aims to demonstrate how design could help interactively visualise data, and how design can lower the threshold of transforming raw data into conprehensive information. It could be helpful not only to the citizens, but also to the government employees who need to make data-based reports. This transformation could also provide a basis for strengthening civil society. </p>\n<hr>\n<img style=\"\" src=\"/img-5-c8b4b3dc590efc64e172de9bc893fcb0.gif\" alt=\"The concept of platform hosting the livable experience of Taiwanese design.\">\n<hr>\n<p>The documentation of this project is illustrated with the Double Diamond model. </p>\n<h2>Discover</h2>\n<p><strong>Image of the persona</strong></p>\n<hr>\n<figure class=\"grid-image\"><div class=\"grid-image-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 100.06250000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"persona 01\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/persona-01-740a96aae403fd6c6e89e7cc2fe587de-8a74c.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/persona-01-740a96aae403fd6c6e89e7cc2fe587de-9895e.png 500w,\n/static/persona-01-740a96aae403fd6c6e89e7cc2fe587de-3f30e.png 1000w,\n/static/persona-01-740a96aae403fd6c6e89e7cc2fe587de-8a74c.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 134.4375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"persona 02\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/persona-02-fa68beb7b1e4ccf34f12ead08290157c-8a74c.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/persona-02-fa68beb7b1e4ccf34f12ead08290157c-9895e.png 500w,\n/static/persona-02-fa68beb7b1e4ccf34f12ead08290157c-3f30e.png 1000w,\n/static/persona-02-fa68beb7b1e4ccf34f12ead08290157c-8a74c.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n</div></figure>\n<h2>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100.06250000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"persona no.2\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/persona-03-6dff8c4eede5ca5d530b69a2ca93fb33-8a74c.png\" srcset=\"/static/persona-03-6dff8c4eede5ca5d530b69a2ca93fb33-9895e.png 500w,\n/static/persona-03-6dff8c4eede5ca5d530b69a2ca93fb33-3f30e.png 1000w,\n/static/persona-03-6dff8c4eede5ca5d530b69a2ca93fb33-8a74c.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </h2>\n<p>This design project was the term assignment of a 3-week intense course at Aalto University. Given the limitation of time, the research is mainly based on my <em>auto</em> ethnographical usage experience and desktop research. While working on this, I had several times of tutoring with the teachers of the Information Design course, Juuso Koponen and Jonatan Hildén. They gave me many enlightening insights from their perspectives as professional users of Statfin.</p>\n<p>Another source of information was a guest lecture given during the Information Design course by Anne-Mari Kiviniemi, the spokesperson and communication manager Terveyden ja hyvinvoinnin laitos (THL). She shared her experience of facilitating abilities in data visualisation in her department. They made a huge effort on learning how to use online infographic makers and Microsoft Excel to make their statistical data looks more comprehensive and attractive. It made me realize that not only the citizens need to transform data, but also many government employees use the official statistical data frequently to make reports and slides for communication. </p>\n<p>The main research finding is threefold: Firstly, I establish an overall understanding of the national statistical system of Finland, therefore, some organisational factors lay behind the current service gaps could be identify; secondly, I studied the common criteria to assess the quality of the official statistics, and thus have a glimpse on how statistical authorities evaluate the performance of themselves; thirdly, I acquired a basic understanding of the stakeholders in this field and established the benchmarks for this design project.\nThe finding is shown in the following section, Redesign Statfin.</p>\n<h2>Define</h2>\n<p>Intro to the group defined </p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 74.93734335839599%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Customer Journey Map\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/customer-map-172def69b67125bd51eda809c34b2207-35db6.png\" srcset=\"/static/customer-map-172def69b67125bd51eda809c34b2207-8ae0f.png 500w,\n/static/customer-map-172def69b67125bd51eda809c34b2207-0b81a.png 1000w,\n/static/customer-map-172def69b67125bd51eda809c34b2207-35db6.png 2000w,\n/static/customer-map-172def69b67125bd51eda809c34b2207-ff514.png 2394w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Customer Journey Map</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p>The gap between the groups of users</p>\n<h2>Develop</h2>\n<h4>Design Principle</h4>\n<p>The project of redesign statfin is based on the three principles, which are categorized based on the observation of the current problems mentioned.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1089px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 19.008264462809915%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"the design principles\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/principles-18f3682fc5b36641406074fc63018b29-37450.png\" srcset=\"/static/principles-18f3682fc5b36641406074fc63018b29-8227e.png 500w,\n/static/principles-18f3682fc5b36641406074fc63018b29-95c54.png 1000w,\n/static/principles-18f3682fc5b36641406074fc63018b29-37450.png 1089w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1089px) 100vw, 1089px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Visualisation First</strong>: Always visualise raw data at the first glance, than provide tools for further investigation.</li>\n<li><strong>Intuitive Interaction</strong>: Reduce cognitive load and keep the interface intuitive and effective.</li>\n<li><strong>Seamless Experience</strong>: Make experience consistent while producing, interacting, and viewing information.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Sitemap and value proposition</h4>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 74.93734335839599%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Sitemap and values that the redesign provides\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/sitemap-6d90bf5c41beeafa07187f1c4f00fadc-35db6.png\" srcset=\"/static/sitemap-6d90bf5c41beeafa07187f1c4f00fadc-8ae0f.png 500w,\n/static/sitemap-6d90bf5c41beeafa07187f1c4f00fadc-0b81a.png 1000w,\n/static/sitemap-6d90bf5c41beeafa07187f1c4f00fadc-35db6.png 2000w,\n/static/sitemap-6d90bf5c41beeafa07187f1c4f00fadc-ff514.png 2394w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Sitemap and values that the redesign provides</figcaption>\n<p>Interactive??</p>\n<h2>Deliver</h2>\n<p>A great amount of data is released by governments, yet there is few common standards established on how to assess its usabilities. Taking official statistics as an example, most of the common measurement methods focus merely on the quality of statistical data, such as the indicators (e.g. Relevance of Concept, Accuracy of Estimates, Timeliness and Punctuality in Disseminating Results, etc) used by Eurostat and by the OECD.</p>\n<p>How “data” can be used as valuable “information” is equally important as the the accessibility of data (Kenett &#x26; Shmueli, 2016). A good quality of official statistical data doesn’t guarantee qualified use/transformation of data. The current measurement for assessment may be just beneficial for the professionals who are familiar with how to utilise raw data for further analysis.</p>\n<h5>Showcase</h5>\n<p>This was a showcase work at Visualizing Knowledge 2018 Conference, Finland. </p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1440px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 57.847222222222214%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"a screenshot of the showcase\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/img-2-535a2c2fbb329c8f925b5d5169e95f0b-daa98.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/img-2-535a2c2fbb329c8f925b5d5169e95f0b-09631.jpg 500w,\n/static/img-2-535a2c2fbb329c8f925b5d5169e95f0b-d85d3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/img-2-535a2c2fbb329c8f925b5d5169e95f0b-daa98.jpg 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figure class=\"grid-image\"><div class=\"grid-image-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1302px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.58986175115209%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"img 3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/img-3-150531a923cbb14f779a93e30abea2a5-5f8e5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/img-3-150531a923cbb14f779a93e30abea2a5-97180.jpg 500w,\n/static/img-3-150531a923cbb14f779a93e30abea2a5-5b02c.jpg 1000w,\n/static/img-3-150531a923cbb14f779a93e30abea2a5-5f8e5.jpg 1302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1302px) 100vw, 1302px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1215px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"img 4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/img-4-dfb27d511b4ad9dce3f51b9dc6c00b4f-6418a.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/img-4-dfb27d511b4ad9dce3f51b9dc6c00b4f-35acd.jpg 500w,\n/static/img-4-dfb27d511b4ad9dce3f51b9dc6c00b4f-5e558.jpg 1000w,\n/static/img-4-dfb27d511b4ad9dce3f51b9dc6c00b4f-6418a.jpg 1215w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1215px) 100vw, 1215px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n</div></figure>\n<hr>\n<p>You can visit <a href=\"https://yentsenliu.com/redesign_statfin/\" target=\"blank\">the webpage showcasing the work</a> at Visualizing Knowledge 2018 here. (Unfortunately, the mobile version of this page is not availabe because the webpage was designed for showcasing on high resolution display.)</p>\n<hr>\n<img style=\"\" src=\"/img-1-c64ce6302f15d3e0399ea27340737810.gif\" alt=\"The concept of platform hosting the livable experience of Taiwanese design.\">\n<figcaption>A glance at the interface after (left) and before (right) the redesign</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<h5>Report</h5>\n<p>There is also a report introducing the design in details available on <a href=\"https://yentsenliu.gitbook.io/redesign-statfin/\" target=\"blank\">Gitbook</a>.</p>\n<p>I was also invited to have an informal presentation of this work at Statistics Finland (Tilastokeskus), the statistics authority of Finland, in 24th May, 2018.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 31.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"some snap shots of the conference and the visit to Statistics Finland\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-7874f.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-cf602.jpg 500w,\n/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-ec5b1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-7874f.jpg 2000w,\n/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-b35a9.jpg 3000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  ","frontmatter":{"layout":"post","title":"Official Statistics in The Age of Data","path":"/statfin/","category":"design for interface","skill":["UI prototyping & design(Skecth App, Framer)","Front-end development (HTML, SASS, Javascript)","UX (Experience visualisation)"],"role":["UI/UX Design","Front-end Development"],"description":"Showcase work at Visualizing Knowledge 2018 Conference, Finland.","date":"2018","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":500,"height":357,"src":"/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-7f380.jpg","srcSet":"/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-7f380.jpg 1x,\n/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-b4bc2.jpg 1.5x,\n/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-ac12b.jpg 2x","srcWebp":"/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-e6ca4.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-e6ca4.webp 1x,\n/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-4bf37.webp 1.5x,\n/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-0c5e8.webp 2x"},"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3992583436341162,"src":"/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-c391d.jpg","srcSet":"/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-41c10.jpg 200w,\n/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-df9ca.jpg 400w,\n/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-c391d.jpg 800w,\n/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e72f02a9f72dd1e90-10138.jpg 1132w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{}}